CakePHP CSS & JavaScript Minifier.

Please refer to http://garbers.co.za/sandbox/cakephp-javascript-css-minifier/
for instructions on how to install this plugin.
Additionally, you can find this on the CakePHP Bakery, at
http://bakery.cakephp.org/articles/view/script-combiner-helper/

If you do happen to find this helpful, please let me know. I'd love to
know where/how it has been implemented.

You can contact me through http://garbers.co.za/, or directly at
geoff@garbers.co.za.
